The presidential ambition of Comrade Olufemi Ajadi Oguntoyinbo got a fresh boost yesterday as he was decorated by the Vigilante Group of Nigeria (VGN). Ajadi was decorated as the Assistant Commandant, Inter-Governmental Affairs in his jurisdiction, Ogun State. The brief decoration ceremony was conducted by Adedoyin Olanrewaju Nureni, a member of the National Executive Council of VGN. Other High-ranking officers of the VGN present to perform the decoration ceremony were Commander Ajibawo Mattew and Commander Adesanya Gbenga. <img class="wp-image-373783 alignleft" src="//i0.wp.com/leadership.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/ajadi-1-e1650545020232-596x600.jpg?resize=335%2C337&#038;ssl=1" alt="ajadi" width="335" height="337" srcset="//i0.wp.com/leadership.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/ajadi-1-e1650545020232.jpg?resize=596%2C600&amp;ssl=1 596w, //i0.wp.com/leadership.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/ajadi-1-e1650545020232.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, //i0.wp.com/leadership.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/ajadi-1-e1650545020232.jpg?resize=70%2C70&amp;ssl=1 70w, //i0.wp.com/leadership.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/ajadi-1-e1650545020232.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, //i0.wp.com/leadership.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/ajadi-1-e1650545020232.jpg?resize=750%2C755&amp;ssl=1 750w, //i0.wp.com/leadership.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/ajadi-1-e1650545020232.jpg?w=768&amp;ssl=1 768w" sizes="(max-width: 335px) 100vw, 335px" data-recalc-dims="1"> Speaking at the event, Ajadi said he was grateful for the honour. He pledged to do his very best towards lifting the efforts of the VGN in the security architecture of the country. Ajadi also vowed to do all his best to improve the security sector of Nigeria. He said, “Nigeria will become safer when I become the President of Nigeria in 2023.” Ajadi, however, appreciated the leadership of the group for considering him worthy of recognition.